  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3f5f7beebd32ff946991fc33737cd197, type: 2}
    lines:
    - Hello Commander. Today we have got a new mission for you.
    - The intelligence have gathered important information on the movement of enemy
      troops. And it indicates an imminent attack.
    - We must build our defences, fight back and then destoy the enemy forces in
      the region.
    - Good luck Commander.
